== Scaling

=== Scaling Resources

From the *Clusters* Page and selecting the Deployment you can scale the Replica Sets supports

image::scaling.png[width="20%", height="20%"]

=== Select the Replicas

You can then select the number of replicas you wish to either increase or decrease

image::scaling_confirmation.png[width=50%, height=50%]

NOTE: If you want the number of replica sets permanent, be sure to update your yaml file, changes will not be persisted
